To use this code with your specific FEN notation, replace `FEN_STRING` in the `\path[board=black] (0,0) grid (8,8);` line with the desired FEN string. For example, if you want to display the starting position of a chess game, use `rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR` as the FEN string.

